  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK502">
<l>kuṭippiṟantu kuṟṟatti ṉīṅki vaṭuppariyu</l>
<l>nāṇuṭaiyāṉ kaṭṭē teḷivu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>(The king's) choice should (fall) on him, who is of good family, who is free from faults, and who has the modesty which fears the wounds (of sin).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
